{"type":"click","text":"A\n    \n      Assessment instruction copy\n      Add \"¿Cómo responder?\" guidance before each Likert scale — MLQ-10, Compass CAAS-12, Bull's Eye sliders. Non-psychologists have no idea what to do.","choice":"assessment-instructions","id":null,"timestamp":1774385030377}
{"type":"click","text":"B\n    \n      Empty states & onboarding copy\n      Profile page shows \"—\" values with no guidance. Tools lack \"what you'll discover\" framing. First-time users feel lost.","choice":"empty-states","id":null,"timestamp":1774385030693}
{"type":"click","text":"C\n    \n      Email capture wired to tools\n      Newsletter form exists on landing but tools don't capture leads. Add optional email prompt after completing any assessment (tag=tool-completion).","choice":"email-capture","id":null,"timestamp":1774385031060}
{"type":"click","text":"D\n    \n      Profile cross-dimension scoring\n      Profile synthesizer shows raw tool outputs but doesn't compute a unified readiness score or surface contradictions between dimensions.","choice":"profile-scoring","id":null,"timestamp":1774385031454}
{"type":"click","text":"E\n    \n      Result sharing / social proof\n      Scorecard PNG exports exist but there's no \"share to LinkedIn\" deep-link or Twitter card. Hard to spread virally without frictionless sharing.","choice":"share-results","id":null,"timestamp":1774385031909}
{"type":"click","text":"F\n    \n      Progress tracking\n      No visual indicator of \"you've completed 3/7 tools.\" Users don't know how far they are from a complete profile.","choice":"progress-tracking","id":null,"timestamp":1774385033203}
